OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1784663291
OL,3,CThames Water creditors make last-ditch
OL,4,Cbid to avoid nationalisation
OL,6,FThe creditors of Thames Water have
OL,7,Fannounced a series of concessions in
OL,8,Fan attempt to make their rescue plan
OL,9,Fmore politically acceptable and avoid
OL,10,Fthe threat of nationalisation by an
OL,11,FAndy Burnham government.
OL,13,FLondon & Valley Water is a consortium
OL,14,Fof hedge funds and infrastructure
OL,15,Finvestors that has, in effect, been in
OL,16,Fcontrol of Thames since shareholders
OL,17,Fcut their losses in 2024.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
