OL,3,CThames Water creditors make last-ditch
OL,4,Cbid to avoid nationalisation
OL,6,FIn his first speech as prime minister
OL,7,Fon Monday, he pledged to "put life's
OL,8,Fessentials back under stronger public
OL,9,Fcontrol to make them affordable."
OL,11,FThe London & Valley consortium, which
OL,12,Fincludes the hedge funds Elliott,
OL,13,FSilver Point and Apollo, says it has a
OL,14,Fplan to turn the company around and re-
OL,15,Flist it on the stock market in the
OL,16,Fearly 2030s without taxpayer funding
OL,17,For any increase in customer bills
OL,18,Fbeyond those already permitted by
OL,19,FOfwat.
OL,26,@oD@ZOUqD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
