OL,3,CThames Water creditors make last-ditch
OL,4,Cbid to avoid nationalisation
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThe consortium has, however, appealed
OL,12,Fto the Competition and Markets
OL,13,FAuthority over Ofwat's latest price
OL,14,Fdetermination.
OL,16,FIt is seeking a higher allowed rate of
OL,17,Freturn and is also asking the
OL,18,Fregulator to relax some of its
OL,19,Fperformance targets, including those
OL,20,Fon sewage spills, leakage and customer
OL,21,Fservice.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
