PN,31408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1784663291
OL,3,CThames Water creditors make last-ditch
OL,4,Cbid to avoid nationalisation
OL,6,FUnder the proposal, almost half of
OL,7,FThames Water's #21 billion debt would
OL,8,Fbe written off - much of it owed to
OL,9,Fmembers of the consortium themselves -
OL,10,Fwhile #10 billion of new investment
OL,11,Fwould be injected into the business.
OL,13,FThe creditors argue this would put the
OL,14,Fcompany on a sustainable footing and
OL,15,Fdeliver for customers after years of
OL,16,Ffailure without the need for temporary
OL,17,Fpublic ownership.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
